title: C-O Segemyhr Season 1
description: This is an old Swedish TV show that is called C/O Segemyhr, which aired between 1998-2004. I've tried to get it on different torrent sites for quite a long time, but last night I got tired of not getting it so I tried to search for it on YouTube, where I hit the jackpot. I downloaded season 1-3 and this is Season 1 (there is actually a total of five seasons). I decided to upload this TV show because I personally believe we cannot afford to loose this treasure-chest of a 1990's TV shows. I will also upload the two other seasons one by one, also Seasons 1-3 in one simple torrent, so that people can download either all three seasons at once, or just one, or two of the torrents. I will also complete the TV show with the two last season (season 4-5) within a short amount of time.
